        "text_JjMKJN": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Under the CCPA, you have the right to:</p><ul><li>Know what personal information is collected, disclosed, or shared.</li><li>Opt-out of the sale of your personal information.</li><li>Access a copy of the specific data we hold about you.</li><li>Delete your personal information from our records.</li><li>Non-Discrimination: You will never receive different service or pricing for exercising these rights.</li></ul>"
